data.description: Nestled on a sprawling corner lot, this updated house exudes opulence and comfort. With over 3300 square feet of living space, it boasts 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. The inviting living room showcases a cozy fireplace, while the family room provides an additional space for relaxation and entertainment. The heart of the home resides in the large kitchen, adorned with an abundance of gleaming cabinetry, breakfast bar, and a dedicated dining area. The oversized dining room effortlessly accommodates formal gatherings. The primary bedroom is an oasis of tranquility, boasting vaulted ceilings, a double vanity, and large walk-in closet. The fenced-in backyard offers a serene escape, while the oversized attached garage provides ample storage for vehicles and belongings. Located just minutes away from Ball State University. Schedule a showing today!
